dcterms:description: The WeChat dataset is collected from Top Stories of WeChat, where videos are regarded as items. It includes behavior records from one hundred thousand active users over a duration of one week, treating each user's entire behavior sequence as a single session.
dcterms:title: WeChat

dcterms:description: The Yoochoose dataset is obtained from the RecSys Challenge 2015. It contains user behavior sequences that are already segmented into sessions, with all users anonymized. The dataset includes behaviors of purchase and clicking.
dcterms:title: Yoochoose
